{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-15","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Da li pamtite da se glagoli menjaju zavisno od lica na koje se odnose? Ako ne znate, sada znate!</p>\n<p>U prethodnim vežbama, naučio si kako da koristi glagol <span class=\"highlighted-text\">poder</span> da pita kako neko može nešto uraditi za tebe.</p>\n<p>Sada ćete naučiti kako da promenite ovaj glagol da pitate da li <strong>ti</strong> možeš nešto uraditi. Samo je potrebno koristiti strukturu:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Puedo</span> + nepromenljivi glagol + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">...?</span></p>\n<p>Da bismo videli primere:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedo usar la computadora?</span> - Mogu li da koristim računar?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedo usar mi apodo?</span> - Mogu li da koristim moj nadimak?</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>U oba modela, tražite dozvolu za korišćenje računara sa vašim nadimkom, mtawaliwa.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Basti kaže <span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedo usar mi apodo?</span>.</p>\n<p>Ovde, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">puedo</span> je forma za prvu osobu, množinu glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">poder</span>, koja se koristi kada osoba traži dozvolu.</p>\n<p>Struktura prati primer:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Puedo</span> + nepromenljivi glagol + <span class=\"highlighted-text\">...?</span></p>\n<p>U ovom slučaju:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Usar</span> to znači koristiti.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mi apodo</span> radi se o njegovom nadimku.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Dakle, Basti pita da li mu je dozvoljeno da koristi svoj nadimak.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte zvuk/audio za odgovor na pitanje koje je navedeno ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling/task-15"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Basti, šta pita ovde?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Ako može da koristi računar.</p>","feedback":"<p>Nema objašnjenja za <span class=\"highlighted-text\">computadora</span>.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako može da koristi drugi telefon.</p>","feedback":"<p>Nemoj spominjati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">teléfono</span>, niti bilo koju riječ vezanu za telefon.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako može da koristi svoj nadimak.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Ako može da postavi pitanje.</p>","feedback":"<p>Tayari pita pitanje.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"desk.png","characters":[{"character":"Sebastián","position":{"x":50,"y":18,"z":1.5},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"ES_A1_basti_personal_details.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":17.91,"finishTimestamp":19.23},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null},{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":null,"opacity":null,"startTime":1,"finishTime":2.32,"dialogue":{"text":"¿Puedo usar mi apodo?","align":"center"}},{"background":null,"character":"Sebastián","position":null,"opacity":0,"startTime":2.82,"finishTime":null,"dialogue":null}]},"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","tests":[],"title":"Lekcija 15","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-learn-contact-information-and-spelling","dashedName":"task-15","certifi